how many downloads,

00:09:47.919 --> 00:09:49.039
we calculate a score,

00:09:49.039 --> 00:09:50.000
we add them all together

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:51.200
in some weighted average,

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:52.000
we come up with a number.

